    {
      "title": "Choosing the right collection",
      "content": "List (ordered, duplicates): ArrayList for random access, LinkedList for frequent head/tail insert. Set (unique): HashSet for O(1), LinkedHashSet for insertion order, TreeSet for sorted. Map: HashMap for O(1), TreeMap for sorted keys, LinkedHashMap for LRU caches. Queue/Stack: ArrayDeque for both (prefer over Stack/LinkedList). Thread-safe: ConcurrentHashMap, CopyOnWriteArrayList, or Collections.synchronizedXxx()."
